% Placeholder directory for figures.
% Required figures:
%   - architecture_diagram.pdf  (System architecture 4-layer diagram)
%   - dashboard_screenshot.pdf  (Interactive dashboard WebView2 screenshot)
%
% To compile without figures, comment out \includegraphics lines in:
%   - sections/architecture.tex (Figure 1)
%   - sections/case_industrial.tex (Figure 2)
%
% Or create placeholder PDFs:
%   pdflatex -jobname=architecture_diagram "\documentclass{article}\usepackage{tikz}\begin{document}\begin{tikzpicture}\draw(0,0)rectangle(12,8);\node at(6,4){Architecture Diagram Placeholder};\end{tikzpicture}\end{document}"
